<item>
            <title>[WFLY-7097] The constant-role-mapper is not able to handle role name with space in it</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-7097</link>
                <project id="12313721" key="WFLY">WildFly</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Adding a role with a space in the name results in 2 roles (for parts of the name) added. The problem is visible after server reload. E.g. adding role &quot;JBoss Admin&quot; results in 2 roles assigned &quot;JBoss&quot; and &quot;Admin&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Expected behavior&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Spaces in role name must be supported and correctly handled. E.g. After adding &quot;JBoss Admin&quot; and server reload &quot;JBoss Admin&quot; is assigned.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
